		<fdd:adoption>Modest adoption of the combination of Matroska and LPCM. An early example was the open source <a href="https://wiki.archivematica.org/Format_policies">Archivematica</a> project (page now archived). For current details on Archivematica's format policies, see <a href="https://www.archivematica.org/en/docs/archivematica-1.13/user-manual/preservation/preservation-planning/">Archivematica Preservation Planning documentation</a>; LPCM is the preservation encoding for audio and Matroska (MKV) the preservation wrapper format for video files.</fdd:adoption>
